subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams broke Gisela Dulko’s serve and saved six set points in a game featuring 12 deuces, going on to win, 6-3, 7-5, in a second-round match at the Australian Open on Thursday.
